Package com.aionemu.commons.configuration

Interface Summary
PropertyTransformer<T> This insterface represents property transformer, each transformer should implement it.
 

Class Summary
ConfigurableProcessor This class is designed to process classes and interfaces that have fields marked with Property annotation
PropertyTransformerFactory This class is responsible for creating property transformers.
 

Exception Summary
TransformationException This exception is internal for configuration process.
 

Annotation Types Summary
Property This annotation is used to mark field that should be processed by ConfigurableProcessor

This annotation is Documented, all definitions with it will appear in javadoc
